refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 boolopenssl_csr_export_to_file
 OpenSSLCertificateSigningRequeststringcsr
 stringoutput_filename
 boolno_text&true;



 openssl_csr_export_to_file 获取证书签名请求（csr）并将之保存在以 output_filename 命名的 PEM 格式文件中。

&reftitle.parameters;



  &openssl.param.csr;

   output_filename



     输出文件的路径。




   no_text

    &note.openssl.param-notext;

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.0.0

     csr 现在接受 OpenSSLCertificateSigningRequest 实例；之前接受类型
     OpenSSL X.509 CSR 的 &resource;。

  &reftitle.examples;



    openssl_csr_export_to_file() 范例


<?php
$subject = array(
    "commonName" => "example.com",
);
$private_key = openssl_pkey_new(array(
    "private_key_bits" => 2048,
    "private_key_type" => OPENSSL_KEYTYPE_RSA,
));
$csr = openssl_csr_new($subject, $private_key, array('digest_alg' => 'sha384') );
openssl_pkey_export_to_file($private_key, 'example-priv.key');
// Along with the subject, the CSR contains the public key corresponding to the private key
openssl_csr_export_to_file($csr, 'example-csr.pem');
?>
